<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Subscription Canceled</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.name || @user.email %>,</p>

      <p>We're sorry to inform you that your AI Talk Coach subscription has been canceled due to payment issues.</p>

      <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @reason %></p>

      <p>Your subscription will no longer be active, and you won't be able to access premium features.</p>

      <h3>Want to Reactivate?</h3>
      <p>You can easily reactivate your subscription by updating your payment method:</p>

      <a href="<%= @reactivate_url %>" class="button">Reactivate Subscription</a>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reply to this email.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The AI Talk Coach Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>AI Talk Coach | Improve your speaking skills with AI-powered coaching</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
